title: Slender The Arrival (GOG) (Latest Version With 1.5.2 Patch)
description:
Hey guys, here Slender the arrival gog edition. It includes all of the bonus content as while as the 1.5.2 patch. Check below to see what new and enjoy. I will seed for as long as possible


This new version is essentially a new build + DLC. Notable changes are a new creature, expanded beginning of the game and an entirely new ending. 

Changelog (except for Steam-related changes :) 

1.5.2 

-Version number has been corrected from 1.6 back to 1.5 

-Fixed a problem where some of the game times were not being recorded on "Easy" 

-Fixed a bug where incomplete games would show up as completed on "Easy" 

-Fixed a problem with "Into the Abyss" not recording players times 

1.5.1 

-Adjusted sensitivity of joystick input. This will hopefully alleviate any issues with 3rd party controllers causing the player to spin in circles.
